f^{(n)}(x)=\left\{\begin{matrix} -\sin x &n=1,5,9,...\\  -\cos x &n=2,6,10,...\\  \sin x &n=3,7,11,...\\  \cos x &n=0,4,8,12,...  \end{matrix}\right.
f^{(n)}(0)=\left\{\begin{matrix} -1 &n=2,6,10,...\\  1 &n=0,4,8,12 \\  0 &\text{otherwise} \end{matrix}\right.
